item.title: 2019-06-12: AWS Summit Tokyo 2019 Day1
item.description: I attended AWS Summit Tokyo 2019 today. It will be held in 3 days. I’m gonna attend it every days. Keynote (10:00-11:30) The music was loud at the venue and it was like rock concert, so I was a little excited. The opening of keynote was started with movies and dance. It’s completely concert. In this AWS Summit Tokyo 2019, 33,000+ have been registered. AWS has 50% share in cloud business, it’s great.
